overview:
Established in the year 2002, we, “Indore Agro Industries”, are a renowned organization engaged in manufacturing, supplying and trading a comprehensive array of Agriculture and Construction Equipment. Our range includes Sledge Hammer, Iron Tawa, Heavy Hoe, Iron Bucket and Pick Axe. Other products offered in this range are Industrial Tagari, Iron Tasla, Iron Crowbar and PVC Product.

Our Products: Iron Tawa Heavy Hoe Iron Bucket Pick Axe

Our Team: We are fostered by a team of highly qualified and dedicated professionals, which has been playing significant role in our success. Owing to our team’s benevolent efforts, we have been able to provide our clients with qualitative range of Sledge Hammer, Iron Tawa, Heavy Hoe, Iron Bucket, Pick Axe, Industrial Tagari, Iron Tasla, Iron Crowbar and PVC Product.

Our Quality: Being a client-centric organization, we endeavor to provide them with the best-in-class products on continual basis. We precisely adapt uncompromising quality approaches so as to come up with commendable range of Sledge Hammer, Iron Tawa, Heavy Hoe, Iron Bucket, Pick Axe, Industrial Tagari, Iron Tasla, Iron Crowbar and PVC Product.

Our Infrastructure: We possess a sound and sophisticated infrastructure, spread across a vast area. To ensure smooth execution of entire business related activities, we have strategically segregated our setup into different units such as manufacturing, quality testing, designing, warehouse and administration office.
